  "title": "Operations Admin",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are looking for a detail-oriented Operations Admin to support daily business operations and coordination tasks. This role is suitable for individuals who are organised, willing to learn, and comfortable working with basic systems and communication tools. Training will be provided, and prior experience is not mandatory.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Organize and maintain schedules, documents, and internal records to support smooth business operations</li><li>Enter data accurately and generate reports to track operational activities</li><li>Communicate clearly with internal teams and external partners to coordinate tasks and share information</li><li>Follow up on assigned tasks to ensure timely completion and resolve issues promptly</li><li>Perform various administrative and operational duties as needed to support the team</li><li>Use basic computer tools such as WhatsApp, email, Google Docs, and Excel to complete daily tasks</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in administrative or operations roles is a plus but not required</li><li>Demonstrate a positive attitude and take responsibility for assigned work</li><li>Show willingness to learn and adhere to established processes</li></ul>",
